      "id": "082f46e9594c827d",
      "text": "The issue of laptop power packs, grid/solar/diesel generator power and internet access all featured in the meeting of DadaMac today. So when organizations, institutions and individuals are looking for proof of concept of what it takes to get connectivity to the un-served and under-served rural communities of Nigeria, and eleswhere, they need look no further than Fantsuam Foundation."
